{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1043,"text":"Chris Anderson asked me if I could put the last 25 years"},{"time":4608,"text":"of anti-poverty campaigning into 10 minutes for TED."},{"time":9307,"text":"That's an Englishman asking an Irishman to be succinct."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13304,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":15369,"text":"I said, \"Chris, that would take a miracle.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":19942,"text":"He said, \"Bono, wouldn't that be a good use of your messianic complex?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":25097,"text":"So, yeah."},{"time":27118,"text":"Then I thought, let's go even further than 25 years."},{"time":31115,"text":"Let's go back before Christ, three millennia,"},{"time":34850,"text":"to a time when, at least in my head, the journey for justice,"},{"time":39217,"text":"the march against inequality and poverty really began."},{"time":43244,"text":"Three thousand years ago,"},{"time":44727,"text":"civilization just getting started on the banks of the Nile,"},{"time":47780,"text":"some slaves, Jewish shepherds in this instance,"},{"time":51685,"text":"smelling of sheep shit, I guess,"},{"time":54593,"text":"proclaimed to the Pharaoh, sitting high on his throne,"},{"time":59172,"text":"\"We, your majesty-ness, are equal to you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":64656,"text":"And the Pharaoh replies, \"Oh, no."},{"time":68037,"text":"You, your miserableness, have got to be kidding.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":71305,"text":"And they say, \"No, no, that's what it says here"},{"time":75117,"text":"in our holy book.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":77128,"text":"Cut to our century, same country, same pyramids,"},{"time":79956,"text":"another people spreading the same idea"},{"time":82194,"text":"of equality with a different book."},{"time":84185,"text":"This time it's called the Facebook."},{"time":87744,"text":"Crowds are gathered in Tahrir Square."},{"time":89636,"text":"They turn a social network from virtual to actual,"},{"time":92049,"text":"and kind of rebooted the 21st century."},{"time":95539,"text":"Not to undersell how messy and ugly"},{"time":98022,"text":"the aftermath of the Arab Spring has been,"},{"time":100770,"text":"neither to oversell the role of technology,"},{"time":103545,"text":"but these things have given a sense of what's possible"},{"time":106912,"text":"when the age-old model of power, the pyramid,"},{"time":111271,"text":"gets turned upside down, putting the people on top"},{"time":114083,"text":"and the pharaohs of today on the bottom, as it were."},{"time":117883,"text":"It's also shown us that something as powerful"},{"time":120958,"text":"as information and the sharing of it can challenge inequality,"},{"time":124983,"text":"because facts, like people,"},{"time":127946,"text":"want to be free, and when they're free,"},{"time":130296,"text":"liberty is usually around the corner,"},{"time":131967,"text":"even for the poorest of the poor --"},{"time":134639,"text":"facts that can challenge cynicism"},{"time":137184,"text":"and the apathy that leads to inertia,"},{"time":140066,"text":"facts that tell us what's working and,"},{"time":141900,"text":"more importantly, what's not, so we can fix it,"},{"time":144633,"text":"facts that if we hear them and heed them could help us"},{"time":147183,"text":"meet the challenge that Nelson Mandela made"},{"time":150717,"text":"back in 2005,"},{"time":153242,"text":"when he asked us to be that great generation"},{"time":155930,"text":"that overcomes that most awful offense to humanity,"},{"time":158993,"text":"extreme poverty,"},{"time":160968,"text":"facts that build a powerful momentum."}]},{"cues":[{"time":165067,"text":"So I thought, forget the rock opera,"},{"time":167655,"text":"forget the bombast, my usual tricks."},{"time":172781,"text":"The only thing singing today would be the facts,"},{"time":176805,"text":"for I have truly embraced by inner nerd."},{"time":182243,"text":"So exit the rock star."},{"time":188531,"text":"Enter the evidence-based activist, the factivist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":197691,"text":"Because what the facts are telling us"},{"time":202355,"text":"is that the long, slow journey,"},{"time":205632,"text":"humanity's long, slow journey of equality,"},{"time":207924,"text":"is actually speeding up."},{"time":209687,"text":"Look at what's been achieved."},{"time":211771,"text":"Look at the pictures these data sets print."},{"time":215121,"text":"Since the year 2000, since the turn of the millennium,"},{"time":218045,"text":"there are eight million more AIDS patients"},{"time":219939,"text":"getting life-saving antiretroviral drugs."},{"time":222670,"text":"Malaria: There are eight countries in sub-Saharan Africa"},{"time":225907,"text":"that have their death rates cut by 75 percent."},{"time":229558,"text":"For kids under five, child mortality, kids under five,"},{"time":233238,"text":"it's down by 2.65 million a year."},{"time":236658,"text":"That's a rate of 7,256 children's lives saved each day."},{"time":243271,"text":"Wow. Wow. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":248521,"text":"Let's just stop for a second, actually, and think about that."},{"time":250809,"text":"Have you read anything anywhere in the last week"},{"time":254639,"text":"that is remotely as important as that number? Wow."},{"time":258959,"text":"Great news. It drives me nuts"},{"time":262947,"text":"that most people don't seem to know this news."},{"time":265835,"text":"Seven thousand kids a day. Here's two of them."},{"time":268694,"text":"This is Michael and Benedicta,"},{"time":271372,"text":"and they're alive thanks in large part"},{"time":274023,"text":"to Dr. Patricia Asamoah -- she's amazing --"},{"time":277924,"text":"and the Global Fund, which all of you financially support,"},{"time":280894,"text":"whether you know it or not."},{"time":282430,"text":"And the Global Fund provides antiretroviral drugs"},{"time":285348,"text":"that stop mothers from passing HIV to their kids."},{"time":288986,"text":"This fantastic news didn't happen by itself."},{"time":292161,"text":"It was fought for, it was campaigned for,"},{"time":294036,"text":"it was innovated for."},{"time":295707,"text":"And this great news gives birth to even more great news,"},{"time":300936,"text":"because the historic trend is this."},{"time":303816,"text":"The number of people living in back-breaking,"},{"time":306424,"text":"soul-crushing extreme poverty has declined"},{"time":309011,"text":"from 43 percent of the world's population in 1990"},{"time":314101,"text":"to 33 percent by 2000"},{"time":317005,"text":"and then to 21 percent by 2010."},{"time":321776,"text":"Give it up for that. (Applause)"},{"time":326039,"text":"Halved. Halved."}]},{"cues":[{"time":329177,"text":"Now, the rate is still too high -- still too many people"},{"time":333477,"text":"unnecessarily losing their lives."},{"time":335455,"text":"There's still work to do."},{"time":336576,"text":"But it's heart-stopping. It's mind-blowing stuff."},{"time":342228,"text":"And if you live on less than $1.25 a day,"},{"time":346708,"text":"if you live in that kind of poverty,"},{"time":348856,"text":"this is not just data."},{"time":350758,"text":"This is everything."},{"time":352637,"text":"If you're a parent who wants the best for your kids -- and I am --"},{"time":358436,"text":"this rapid transition is a route out of despair and into hope."},{"time":363766,"text":"And guess what? If the trajectory continues,"},{"time":366635,"text":"look where the amount of people living on $1.25 a day"},{"time":371172,"text":"gets to by 2030."},{"time":374804,"text":"Can't be true, can it?"},{"time":378116,"text":"That's what the data is telling us. If the trajectory continues,"},{"time":382504,"text":"we get to, wow, the zero zone."},{"time":387645,"text":"For number-crunchers like us,"},{"time":389120,"text":"that is the erogenous zone,"},{"time":392629,"text":"and it's fair to say that I am, by now,"},{"time":395820,"text":"sexually aroused by the collating of data."},{"time":400869,"text":"So virtual elimination of extreme poverty,"},{"time":406130,"text":"as defined by people living on less than $1.25 a day,"},{"time":409730,"text":"adjusted, of course, for inflation from a 1990 baseline."},{"time":414127,"text":"We do love a good baseline."},{"time":417144,"text":"That's amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":418865,"text":"Now I know that some of you think this progress"},{"time":422765,"text":"is all in Asia or Latin America or"},{"time":425456,"text":"model countries like Brazil --"},{"time":426788,"text":"and who doesn't love a Brazilian model? --"},{"time":429680,"text":"but look at sub-Saharan Africa."},{"time":433790,"text":"There's a collection of 10 countries, some call them the lions,"},{"time":437465,"text":"who in the last decade have had a combination"},{"time":440193,"text":"of 100 percent debt cancellation,"},{"time":441737,"text":"a tripling of aid, a tenfold increase in FDI --"},{"time":444478,"text":"that's foreign direct investment --"},{"time":445933,"text":"which has unlocked a quadrupling of domestic resources -- that's local money --"},{"time":449855,"text":"which, when spent wisely -- that's good governance --"},{"time":452519,"text":"cut childhood mortality by a third,"},{"time":454789,"text":"doubled education completion rates,"},{"time":456496,"text":"and they, too, halved extreme poverty,"},{"time":459600,"text":"and at this rate, these 10 get to zero too."},{"time":464029,"text":"So the pride of lions"},{"time":466282,"text":"is the proof of concept."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468998,"text":"There are all kinds of benefits to this."},{"time":472429,"text":"For a start, you won't have to listen"},{"time":475617,"text":"to an insufferable little jumped-up Jesus like myself."},{"time":479969,"text":"How about that? (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":485177,"text":"And 2028, 2030? It's just around the corner."},{"time":489215,"text":"I mean, it's about three Rolling Stones farewell concerts away."},{"time":493496,"text":"(Laughter) I hope. I'm hoping."},{"time":498823,"text":"Makes us look really young."}]},{"cues":[{"time":502510,"text":"So why aren't we jumping up and down about this?"},{"time":505536,"text":"Well, the opportunity is real, but so is the jeopardy."},{"time":509247,"text":"We can't get this done until we really accept"},{"time":513061,"text":"that we can get this done."},{"time":515536,"text":"Look at this graph."},{"time":517789,"text":"It's called inertia. It's how we screw it up."},{"time":522607,"text":"And the next one is really beautiful."},{"time":524481,"text":"It's called momentum."},{"time":528014,"text":"And it's how we can bend the arc of history"},{"time":532570,"text":"down towards zero,"},{"time":534198,"text":"just doing the things that we know work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":536597,"text":"So inertia versus momentum."},{"time":538642,"text":"There is jeopardy, and of course,"},{"time":541183,"text":"the closer you get, it gets harder."},{"time":543555,"text":"We know the obstacles that are in our way"},{"time":545499,"text":"right now, in difficult times."},{"time":547524,"text":"In fact, today in your capital, in difficult times,"},{"time":552665,"text":"some who mind the nation's purse want to cut"},{"time":555240,"text":"life-saving programs like the Global Fund."},{"time":557645,"text":"But you can do something about that."},{"time":559458,"text":"You can tell politicians"},{"time":561442,"text":"that these cuts [can cost] lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":564348,"text":"Right now today, in Oslo as it happens,"},{"time":567925,"text":"oil companies are fighting to keep secret"},{"time":570292,"text":"their payments to governments"},{"time":571770,"text":"for extracting oil in developing countries."},{"time":575487,"text":"You can do something about that too."},{"time":577206,"text":"You can join the One Campaign,"},{"time":579066,"text":"and leaders like Mo Ibrahim, the telecom entrepreneur."},{"time":583419,"text":"We're pushing for laws that make sure that at least some"},{"time":587242,"text":"of the wealth under the ground"},{"time":589714,"text":"ends up in the hands of the people living above it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":593285,"text":"And right now, we know"},{"time":597052,"text":"that the biggest disease of all"},{"time":600764,"text":"is not a disease. It's corruption."},{"time":603727,"text":"But there's a vaccine for that too."},{"time":605551,"text":"It's called transparency, open data sets,"},{"time":609042,"text":"something the TED community is really on it."},{"time":614053,"text":"Daylight, you could call it, transparency."},{"time":617665,"text":"And technology is really turbocharging this."},{"time":620227,"text":"It's getting harder to hide if you're doing bad stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":624978,"text":"So let me tell you about the U-report,"},{"time":627960,"text":"which I'm really excited about. It's 150,000 millennials"},{"time":631567,"text":"all across Uganda, young people"},{"time":633902,"text":"armed with 2G phones, an SMS social network"},{"time":638278,"text":"exposing government corruption"},{"time":641344,"text":"and demanding to know what's in the budget"},{"time":643940,"text":"and how their money is being spent."},{"time":646803,"text":"This is exciting stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":649478,"text":"Look, once you have these tools,"},{"time":652841,"text":"you can't not use them."},{"time":654565,"text":"Once you have this knowledge, you can't un-know it."},{"time":657091,"text":"You can't delete this data from your brain,"},{"time":660366,"text":"but you can delete the cliched image"},{"time":663189,"text":"of supplicant, impoverished peoples"},{"time":665427,"text":"not taking control of their own lives."},{"time":667499,"text":"You can erase that, you really can,"},{"time":669881,"text":"because it's not true anymore. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":675358,"text":"It's transformational."},{"time":678210,"text":"2030? By 2030, robots,"},{"time":682083,"text":"not just serving us Guinness, but drinking it."},{"time":684877,"text":"By the time we get there,"},{"time":687011,"text":"every place with a rough semblance of governance"},{"time":690140,"text":"might actually be on their way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":694170,"text":"So I'm here to -- I guess we're here"},{"time":697975,"text":"to try and infect you with this virtuous, data-based virus,"},{"time":703483,"text":"the one we call factivism."},{"time":705533,"text":"It's not going to kill you."},{"time":707177,"text":"In fact, it could save countless lives."},{"time":711270,"text":"I guess we in the One Campaign would love you"},{"time":713949,"text":"to be contagious, spread it, share it, pass it on."},{"time":718986,"text":"By doing so, you will join us and countless others"},{"time":724196,"text":"in what I truly believe is the greatest adventure ever taken,"},{"time":729159,"text":"the ever-demanding journey of equality."},{"time":733397,"text":"Could we really be the great generation"},{"time":736634,"text":"that Mandela asked us to be?"},{"time":738595,"text":"Might we answer that clarion call with science,"},{"time":742575,"text":"with reason, with facts,"},{"time":745234,"text":"and, dare I say it, emotions?"},{"time":749272,"text":"Because as is obvious, factivists have feelings too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":755404,"text":"I'm thinking of Wael Ghonim, though."},{"time":757891,"text":"Some of you know him. He set up one of the Facebook groups"},{"time":760166,"text":"behind the Tahrir Square in Cairo."},{"time":764269,"text":"He got thrown in jail for it,"},{"time":765819,"text":"but I have his words tattooed on my brain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":770542,"text":"\"We are going to win because we don't understand politics."},{"time":775029,"text":"We are going to win because we don't play their dirty games."},{"time":778154,"text":"We are going to win because we don't have a party political agenda."},{"time":781442,"text":"We are going to win because the tears"},{"time":783413,"text":"that come from our eyes actually come from our hearts."},{"time":786519,"text":"We are going to win because we have dreams,"},{"time":789383,"text":"and we're willing to stand up for those dreams.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":792893,"text":"Wael is right."},{"time":795206,"text":"We're going to win"},{"time":797068,"text":"if we work together as one,"},{"time":799300,"text":"because the power of the people"},{"time":801744,"text":"is so much stronger than the people in power."}]},{"cues":[{"time":805568,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":809018,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":811890,"text":"Thank you so much. (Applause)"}]}]}